WEBVTT

00:03:29.737 --> 00:03:31.073
"One of the great achievements

00:03:31.073 --> 00:03:33.329
in military engineering of the 20th century."

00:03:33.329 --> 00:03:35.159
The trail is a testimony to the strength of will

00:03:35.159 --> 00:03:36.285
of the Vietnamese people,

00:03:36.285 --> 00:03:37.795
and the men and women who used the trail

00:03:37.795 --> 00:03:39.496
have become folk heros.